cff-version: 1.2.0
message: "If you use or reference QONTOS in your work, please cite it using this metadata."
type: software
title: "QONTOS: Quantum Orchestrated Network for Transformative Optimization Systems"
abstract: >-
  QONTOS is a full-stack quantum computing platform combining modular
  tantalum-silicon qubit hardware, photonic interconnects, AI-driven error
  decoding, and a cloud-native software stack. This repository contains the
  public research papers, whitepapers, and roadmap documents.
authors:
